      "wmPackages": "Package purchase records for Wealth Managers. Each package belongs to a tier (bronze/silver/gold/platinum) with a fixed number of will credits, validity period, and pricing."
    },
    "relationships": [
      "Each WealthManager has many WalletTransactions, FollowUps, TeamMembers, Customers, and Packages",
      "Each WalletTransaction may reference a Customer (for will_used) or a Package (for package_purchase)",
      "Each WMCustomer links to Cases and Services tagged under the WM",
      "Each WMTeamMember belongs to a WealthManager",
      "Each WMPackage belongs to a WealthManager and tracks will credits used/remaining"
    ]
